headline: 2 Quantum Computing Stocks to Buy Right Now
summary: Quantum computing represents the next technological frontier, potentially revolutionizing fields from drug discovery to cybersecurity.  The global quantum computing market is expected to grow exponentially in the coming decades.  In 1981, Nobel Prize-winning physicist Richard Feynman first proposed the concept of quantum computers, recognizing that classical machines could never efficiently simulate quantum systems.
